  prototype={<>void DWARFLinkerImpl::addObjectFile (<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarf-linker/dwarffile">DWARFFile</a> &amp; File, <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarf-linker/dwarflinkerbase/#abdf3094623b3752dabeeb5bd7ceb24ad">ObjFileLoaderTy</a> Loader=nullptr, <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarf-linker/dwarflinkerbase/#a537122974e714f93e8ad5fa29439e856">CompileUnitHandlerTy</a> OnCUDieLoaded=&#91;&#93;(<a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/target/lib/target/aarch64/aarch64promoteconstant-cpp/#a90f8350fecae261c25be85d38b451bff">const</a> <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarfunit">DWARFUnit</a> &amp;) &#123;&#125;)</>}
  labels = {["virtual"]}>
Add object file to be linked.

Pre-load compile unit die. Call <code>OnCUDieLoaded</code> for each compile unit die. If specified <code>File</code> has reference to the Clang module then such module would be pre-loaded by <code>Loader</code> for !Update case.


<SectionUser title="Precondition">
NoODR, Update options should be set before call to addObjectFile.
</SectionUser>
